  ('EX157','Draw Stroke & Pry Technique','Technical / Skill','Canoeing','Lateral control; draws and pries are the primary boat positioning tools at docks, in current, and for obstacle avoidance','Critical','0B-v1.6.6','2026-06-10T17:40:05.453426+00:00'::timestamptz),
