  ('EX183','Running with Poles (Trail / Ultra)','Technical / Skill','Mountain Running / Sky Running','Poles are permitted in most mountain running formats above 50k and some sky races; uphill pole technique adds 5–10% speed on sustained climbs and reduces quad load on technical descents','High','0B-v1.6.6','2026-06-10T17:40:05.453426+00:00'::timestamptz),
