  ('Duathlon','D-006','Road Cycling','Primary',42.0,50.0,42.0,52.0,40.0,50.0,35.0,45.0,'Highest allocation by race time (~57%). Lower injury risk than running supports higher volume. Must include R1→Bike T1 simulation AND long rides for aerobic base.  SESSIONS/WEEK: Base: 3 | Build: 3–4 | Peak: 3–4 | Taper: 2–3 BIKE PACING: Train at 75–80% FTP in race simulation sessions. High-cadence final segments (last 3–5km) before every T2 brick run.','included','Highest allocation by race time (~57%).','Lower injury risk than running supports higher volume. | Must include R1→Bike T1 simulation AND long rides for aerobic base. | SESSIONS/WEEK: Base: 3 | Build: 3–4 | Peak: 3–4 | Taper: 2–3 | BIKE PACING: Train at 75–80% FTP in race simulation sessions. | High-cadence final segments (last 3–5km) before every T2 brick run.','Highest allocation by race time (~57%). Lower injury risk than running supports higher volume. Must include R1→Bike T1 simulation AND long rides for aerobic base.

