  ('Triathlon (Half / 70.3)','Base',10.0,14.0,'WEEKLY TARGET HOURS: BASE: 10–14 hrs | BUILD: 12–18 hrs | PEAK: 14–20 hrs | TAPER: 8–10 hrs

80/20 INTENSITY: 80% genuinely easy. Grey-zone training (moderate) at Half IM volume = accumulated fatigue without corresponding adaptation. Consistent training at 85–90% of target volume beats sporadic peak weeks. NUTRITION REHEARSAL: Practice race-day nutrition strategy on every long bike (60g+ carbs/hr) and every brick run from Build onward. Race-day nutrition surprises are preventable.','hrs','0A-v1.6.6','2026-06-10T17:40:05.453426+00:00'::timestamptz),
