  ('Long Distance / Endurance Cycling (Enduro)','Base',8.0,12.0,'WEEKLY TARGET HOURS: BASE: 8–12 hrs | BUILD: 10–16 hrs | PEAK: 10–16 hrs | TAPER: 5–8 hrs

