  ('Canoe / Kayak Marathon (Ultra-Distance)','Base',10.0,14.0,'WEEKLY TARGET HOURS: BASE: 10–14 hrs | BUILD: 14–18 hrs | PEAK: 16–22 hrs | TAPER: 6–9 hrs

